01:10:48,708 --> 01:10:50,000
Faites demi-tour.

447
01:10:50,792 --> 01:10:51,958
Repartez !

448
01:10:58,458 --> 01:10:59,458
Noa !

449
01:11:02,875 --> 01:11:04,083
Mae !

450
01:11:09,542 --> 01:11:10,542
Mae !

451
01:11:10,917 --> 01:11:11,917
Non !

