01:11:26,958 --> 01:11:27,958
Mae !

453
01:11:32,375 --> 01:11:33,375
Accroche-toi !

454
01:11:34,000 --> 01:11:35,583
Mae !

455
01:11:50,833 --> 01:11:52,333
Non ! Raka !

456
01:11:52,500 --> 01:11:53,500
Raka !

457
01:12:07,667 --> 01:12:08,917
Ensemble,

458
01:12:10,083 --> 01:12:11,250
